by even curing the sick.

267
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:49,570
It also makes the food taste better.

268
00:21:49,970 --> 00:21:51,370
I see.

269
00:21:53,240 --> 00:21:55,410
-You can eat it now.
-Okay.

270
00:21:59,480 --> 00:22:01,650
Also, take this.

271
00:22:02,480 --> 00:22:05,220
You can give this to Sang-mi
and your wife.

272
00:22:05,650 --> 00:22:09,160
I'm sure they haven't been able to
eat properly either.

273
00:22:10,560 --> 00:22:11,890
But,

274
00:22:13,390 --> 00:22:16,000
why are you being so nice to us?

275
00:22:17,930 --> 00:22:19,670
We have nothing to give back to you.

276
00:22:20,970 --> 00:22:22,240
Because he exists.

277
00:22:23,770 --> 00:22:26,470
-Pardon?
-We didn't meet you

278
00:22:26,940 --> 00:22:28,710
by coincidence.

279
00:22:29,140 --> 00:22:32,980
Everything that happens to us
is a message from Almighty.

280
00:22:33,710 --> 00:22:35,620
Our Almighty told us to

281
00:22:35,720 --> 00:22:40,050
take care of our troubled brethren
as if they were our own family.

282
00:22:40,790 --> 00:22:44,430
I'm sure Almighty is trying to
tell you something too.

283
00:22:44,760 --> 00:22:47,430
It's just that we're not able to
see what that is yet.

284
00:22:48,460 --> 00:22:50,130
So try to pay close attention.

285
00:23:09,020 --> 00:23:10,080
