286
00:23:10,150 --> 00:23:12,450
-He did it!
-He won!

287
00:23:12,820 --> 00:23:17,790
-Han Yong-min!
-Han Yong-min!

288
00:23:17,860 --> 00:23:20,960
-Han Yong-min!
-Han Yong-min!

289
00:23:21,030 --> 00:23:23,160
-Han Yong-min!
